### Health (nodes + serviceLevel)
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Trip history (READ) — SOUTH
GET http://localhost:3000/trips/history?latitude=10.77

### Trip history (READ) — NORTH
GET http://localhost:3000/trips/history?latitude=21.03

### Book trip (WRITE) — SOUTH (should fail with 503 when south primary is down)
POST http://localhost:3000/trips/book
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 10.77,
  "note": "demo booking from requests.http"
}

### Book trip (WRITE) — NORTH (should fail with 503 when north primary is down)
POST http://localhost:3000/trips/book
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 21.03,
  "note": "demo booking from requests.http"
}

